occurrenceRemarks: Shrub to 3m. Leaves strongly coriaceous, dark glossy green above, paler beneath. Outher tepals yellow green; inner yellowish with deep crimson base. Anthers crimson, stigmas pale. Fruit grey-green.; Caatinga.
